===Noun phrase===
'''[[ethical]] [[dative]]'''
#{{grammar}} a form of the [[dative case]] applied to [[pronoun]]s; used (in [[Latin]] and some other languages, but rare in [[English]]) to show a certain interest felt by the person indicated
#:Example. "I'll rhyme ''you'' so eight years together," - As You Like It, iii. 2.
